title: UK based Developer for Trading Algorithm
author: JaySince1992
text:
I have been trading Fx and commodities for ~7 years, my approach is predominately Swing to Position trading in the direction of macro-sentiment. I typically trade pairs with the largest divergence for volatility and have a few strategies that I am interesting in automating.

I know several traders… some more IT savvy than others, but I would like to team up with someone is is based in the UK, technical and ideally has an interest in the markets. 

I am obviously happy to share my knowledge and network to support the project.

Ideal languages would be MQL5 or PineScript… however if you already know these, then it’s likely you are already codings algorithms, so Python/C etc. would be good.

Feel free to drop me a note if you are interested in finding out more.
